''[[Employee of the Month (podcast)|'''Employee of the Month''']]'' is a talk show about dreamy careers. The host, [[Catie Lazarus]], gives each guest the Employee of the Month Award. Each installment features guests with jobs of interest, ranging from television personalities and musicians to comedians and puppeteers.

