{{italic title}}
'''''Outdoor USA Magazine''''' is a paper and online [[trade publication]] for the [[North America]]n [[outdoor industry]]. The magazine is distributed to outdoor [[retailer]]s, [[manufacturer]]s, [[sales representative]]s and other industry [[Stakeholder (corporate)|stakeholder]]s. As a trade publication it reports on news relevant to its industry.<ref name="oia">{{cite news|title=Outdoor USA Magazine Announces the Inaugural Top 100 Retailers List|url=https://outdoorindustry.org/press-release/outdoor-usa-magazine-announces-the-inaugural-top-100-retailers-list/|accessdate=22 April 2017|work=Outdoor Industry Association|date=26 August 2014|location=Santa Clara, California}}</ref> It is published on a monthly basis.<ref name="oia"/>

